Package com.github.tadukoo.util.view.font

Classes for dealing with Fonts. See FontFamily and FontResourceLoader for more information, and see the FontFamilies enum for a collection of FontFamilies that can be used when using Tadukoo Fonts.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FontConstants
    Contains constants for common strings found in font file names
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FontFamily
    Represents a single font family.
    FontResourceLoader
    Font Resource Loader is used to load Font Families.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FontFamilies
    Contains an enumeration of FontFamilies supported via use of the Tadukoo Fonts project.
